            </div>
        </div>
            
        <div>
            <h1 class="text-xl h-25vh">The ultimate API for programming questions. Access random and AI-generated questions to enhance your coding skills.</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mx-auto text-white">
            
            <h1 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mt-20 mb-10" >GETTING STARTED</h1>
            <div class="m-6 w-6/12 mx-auto flex flex-col gap-8 border-4 border-primaryGreen bg-backgroundGreen p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">             
                <h1 class="text-white">Challenge your knowledge <a class="hover:text-primaryGreen hover:underline hover:decoration-2" href="/daily-question">here!</a></h1>                
                <h1 class="text-white">Find out more <a class="hover:text-primaryGreen hover:underline hover:decoration-2" href="/about-us">about the team</a></h1>            
